id: pm-peyv
title: Config-driven optional close reason via governance.require_close_reason
description: "pm close hard-requires a non-empty reason; for solo repos / agent automation the history record can suffice. A settings key (default true = no change) relaxes it, mirroring the validate-close config pattern."
